{"tid":1739684,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑post 左篇文 5分鐘就下架","createTime":"2019-11-19T16:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T19:52:58.000Z","uid":313426,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed1cbd586546688ed4722d7c0f7fbb409cdb76b","tid":1739684,"uid":313426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"陶傑 Channel 剛剛 post 左此文, 無 5分鐘就下架, 咁就要開心 share :<br />\n<br />\n原來連朱鎔基的孫女朱媛小姐也參加了反修例抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超定性：困在理工大學裏的五百人，全部犯了暴動罪！那麼連朱鎔基的孫女也是暴徒。啊，不是真的吧？希望是外國勢力散佈的假消息，請林鄭特府盡快闢謠。<br />\n<br />\n不過據說幸好在曾前主席等雷霆救兵不顧生命安危、午夜闖校營救之下，警方停止進攻，朱小公主終於脫險。曾主席和前線警員辛苦了！<br />\n<br />\n其實何須勞動曾主席，只要林鄭親自打一個電話給指揮官，告訴他通知前線警員，重點找朱孫女放出即可。估計毅進畢業，97前後出生的警察，與全香港大學生一樣，不會知道朱鎔基是誰。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，大家現在知道了。希望警方棍下留情，人性化處理。<br />\n<br />\n還是李嘉誠先生眼光獨到，早就呼籲你林鄭對年輕人「網開一面」，你看，真的不網開一面不行，請林鄭政府全力護送朱小姐安全北歸。<br />\n<br />\n朱鎔基總理曾經說：香港回歸之後，港人治港，如果管理不好，不但你們有責任，我們也有責任。<br />\n<br />\n當年此人性化的發言，贏得香港人讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n若孫女來香港後也學壞了，不知尚健在的爺爺有責任否？"},{"pid":"5d5183fc9ea8a23836fd1cbd1260a233fb06b92c","tid":1739684,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37eea55e4b487fbb8afeaa11f28a77c610d1efd7","tid":1739684,"uid":270357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"陶傑真係好撚仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3a90cc19e15fea06866d4f3bcd6e36d2e4815f","tid":1739684,"uid":313426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxxqeRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxxqeRh.jpg&h=8781a66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家得呢篇"},{"pid":"b9e93b27897fff5374eef42843f7831d8f516d48","tid":1739684,"uid":295699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c3a90cc19e15fea06866d4f3bcd6e36d2e4815f","tid":1739684,"uid":313426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxxqeRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxxqeRh.jpg&h=8781a66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家得呢篇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025e3fcfc879d3133911138e77a23f3fb0df7846","tid":1739684,"uid":1247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:29:23.000Z","msg":"即係點 <br />\n扮講中左定真係講中左<br />\n<br />\n我睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5378f6c7895e31bc36b4a7c18a1c0015f370145d","tid":1739684,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:49:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1e80c09243ec718b38c917b23d42e32fc3c11c41","tid":1739684,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c3a90cc19e15fea06866d4f3bcd6e36d2e4815f","tid":1739684,"uid":313426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxxqeRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxxqeRh.jpg&h=8781a66b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家得呢篇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:52:58.000Z","msg":"19擺到明唔